{"tid":858961,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好中意黑色子彈?","createTime":"2018-10-12T07:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T08:07:26.000Z","uid":215534,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d2ee44e653ac07f4d3973ae20d1d5a941b94d7","tid":858961,"uid":215534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:22:10.000Z","msg":"記得以前睇動畫 雖然畫風又崩又唔穩定 節奏又差 但勝在設定唔錯 所以我買左小說嚟睇<br />\n開始睇小說就好似上左癮咁 每次睇到啲好虐既劇情個心就會扯住扯住咁 成個人都好唔舒服<br />\n神崎紫電每次都將劇情寫到好有意境 單單係第一集個序講人類戰敗 蓮太郎比天童收養嗰到已經好震撼 伏筆又夠哂隱晦<br />\n以末日為題 又加入唔同元素咁<br />\n插圖畫風雖然唔主流 但係喺構圖同用色就真係好靚<br />\n其中我最中意醫生 表面上係搞笑角色同比情報 但其實係全套野最了解蓮太郎既人<br />\n出得7集 神崎紫電條契弟就人間蒸發左 仲喺本得170頁既第七集個後記仲話咩因為想劇情連貫啲特登寫咁少 仲叫讀者期待下一集 每次諗返起都想放火燒佢全家<br />\n聽講作者炒股票發左達唔寫都唔知堅定流 如果我中六合彩一定買起佢迫佢繼續寫<br />\n不過其實過左咁耐 作為小說一早上左我心入面既神枱 可能一切都係昔日幼稚既我睇得爽就自己不斷美化 吹捧<br />\n身邊既朋友知冇再出 都唔肯嘥時間睇<br />\n唔知仲有冇同好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d936ef7011f000fccfd24fc4d609cc6f4791d3","tid":858961,"uid":152114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"我睇套野係為咗聽佢動漫個ed"},{"pid":"f01de65b1f5f112f9d22374375b487922ede12cc","tid":858961,"uid":98507,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:08.000Z","msg":"只想想講一句<br />\n<br />\n虐蘿莉正仆街屌你老母快撚d去死"},{"pid":"206ae01e561fe4fa21228f862adc6ec5ea6487fc","tid":858961,"uid":215534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:26.000Z","msg":"睇小說啦"},{"pid":"3c757f933fb21b1e7e21cf369f98aab043ea40f3","tid":858961,"uid":215534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f01de65b1f5f112f9d22374375b487922ede12cc","tid":858961,"uid":98507,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:08.000Z","msg":"只想想講一句<br />\n<br />\n虐蘿莉正仆街屌你老母快撚d去死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"主角都成日比人虐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00f86a1719ec9bfdc5179065489f4e0102d719","tid":858961,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"第4集就做到大結局咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67db432add8a27db8e9ab36e62dba1e8234464f","tid":858961,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/183641_62ef16b99ebb52806b3c92f272d15139.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F183641_62ef16b99ebb52806b3c92f272d15139.gif&h=0c0752d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72eebbb3bbb0d7afc0b9fab9dc9026cd1ea0aba6","tid":858961,"uid":215534,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"果然過氣小說冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4043822b6fbae449279e882590b0e349c8194b","tid":858961,"uid":207038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"Hai meh"},{"pid":"e7fef631e1eb6b4f0073160f44353973471a6f3a","tid":858961,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"呢套連有生之年都談唔上<br />\n係直頭冇尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c862ce79cf8cdffd570a22a8f907b2388e93a7","tid":858961,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01de65b1f5f112f9d22374375b487922ede12cc","tid":858961,"uid":98507,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:08.000Z","msg":"只想想講一句<br />\n<br />\n虐蘿莉正仆街屌你老母快撚d去死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"agger！"},{"pid":"d0cff8fbd